metadata.name: Dive
metadata.description:
This piece was made using traditional painting techniques in a hyperrealistic style on Procreate. The entire 3-piece collection took over 150 hours to complete. 

Image size 5906 px x 7875 px 

Artist-signed physical print 50 x 65 cm (with 3 cm border)

Digital painting on Procreate

Talloires-Montmin, France | 2022
